rdfs:label: SMETANA
ns:common.topic.description: SMETANA, the Self-Modifying Extremely Tiny AutomatoN Application, is a language operating on a series of steps, with two instructions. It was invented around 1994 by Chris Pressey. \"Smetana\" means \"sour cream\" in russian and ukrainian languages
